measurements.description: Five flowers on one 18-cm pendent inflorescence and one immature inflorescence; sepals flat, rich yellow heavialy spotted cordovan; petals completely reflexed, rich yellow heavily spotted cordovan; hypochile rich yellow marked dark cordovan, 2.9 cm x 4.0 cm, epichile, 3.3 cm x 3.8 cm, and horns translucent ivory spotted cordovan; column green spotted cordovan, wings ivory spotted cordovan; anther cap yellow; substance very firm; texture matte, lip glossy.
